{"tid":952058,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一樣自己視之如寶的收藏","createTime":"2018-12-22T19:32:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T22:15:28.000Z","uid":42164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e379df10f2e26248f2355ed4867224ff9086fda0","tid":952058,"uid":42164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T19:32:40.000Z","msg":"利申，純粹希望大家分享下自己鍾意既嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望巴絲們唔好judge人哋既喜好<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前排颱風季，屋企窗台滲水，流到地板濕曬，我即時反應係，好驚放喺我間房地下既呢個袋都會濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9t8AOHG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9t8AOHG.jpg&h=0633a92d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OasU4gu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOasU4gu.jpg&h=766187bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個帆布袋入面就係我儲咗幾年既珍藏&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1t4z4gz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1t4z4gz.jpg&h=76024373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hRgFZPY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhRgFZPY.jpg&h=77d64ecc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">BL漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n入面有二手既、喺日本買既、喺信和買既<br />\n<br />\n其中有一套係full set單行本嚟，作者已經畫咗十幾年，由於我係近幾年先迷上，舊嗰幾本就上網買二手（已經有少少發黃&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），之後再出我就拜託朋友喺日本買/我自己去日本旅行時買<br />\n<br />\n因為始終都有啲不雅，唔敢公然放喺書櫃（雖然我屋企人都知知哋我鍾意睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），同埋因為驚再變黃，我就收埋喺個帆布袋到，擺喺房既一個角落，方便自己有時拎出嚟睇<br />\n<br />\n老實講我既漫畫唔算多，但上面講full set嗰套真係我心頭好嚟，我諗就算第時我結婚生仔住入老人院都要帶住佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知咁多位巴絲又有咩珍藏？一齊分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6852aaf7c814816624ffba4513a380029ff087b1","tid":952058,"uid":80787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T22:15:28.000Z","msg":"帶去結婚係諗住比個律師證婚𠴱陣照住讀？"}]}